        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Literature value. The production volume of selenium in Europe is estimated to be 1094 metric tons (based on selenium content) in 2015 (USGS 2017). This value includes the amount listed under "Other countries" in USGS (2017) as this amount includes the production volumes of India, Serbia and Sweden. The production volume of Russia is not included.

Reference:
USGS (2017) Selenium, U.S. Geological Survey, Mineral Commodity Summaries, January 2017, https://minerals.usgs.gov/minerals/pubs/commodity/selenium/mcs-2017-selen.pdf (retrieved on 2017-09-04).</productionVolumeComment>
